title: Fedora Slimbook Linux Laptop Launched 3K Display, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 Ti
description:
Fedora Slimbook Linux laptop announced with Intel Core i7-12700H, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 Ti, up to 64GB RAM, up to 4TB SSD NVMe storage, and Fedora Linux Workstation pre-installed.

title: Raspberry Pi OS Is Now Based on Debian Bookworm, Supports Raspberry Pi 5
description:
A new Raspberry Pi OS release is available for download based on Debian GNU/Linux 12 "Bookworm" series and supporting Raspberry Pi 5, PipeWire, Wayland, and NetworkManager.
